Hadien ba la dep pynjot syndon thiaw ia ka Hima Shillong ha u snem 1834, ka jingpynkhreh ban synshar ia kane ka Bri ka la iaid haduh katta katta, ka jingwan pan ban tih surok na Guwahati sha Sylhet na U Tirot Sing, Nongkhlaw ka dei tang ka buit sianti ban iaid shuwa naba jem. U Bormanik, u syiem ka Hima Shillong u la maham ia u Tirot Sing, hynrei um kohnguh. Sngewsih ban ong, ba baroh arngut ki la jah sutra (ia ka kyntien patok la shu pynthame).
Hynrei haba ngam jylliew shaphang ki "Bhoi", Ka kyrteng Bhoi ka long kaba bakla. Ia ki briew kiba shong ba sah ha ki thain RiBhoi la khot ki "KAREW" ym ki Bhoi.
Ia U Khasi la ju khot da ka kyrteng "Hynniew Trep" kaba thew ia ki hynniew ki jaid kiba wan hiar shane sha pyrthei, katkum ka jingiathuh khana pateng jong U Lum Sohpetbneng.
Ia ka kyntien “Khasi” ka bym ju don ha ka Hima ka It u HynñiewTrep la pyndonkam ka sorkar phareng ban bit ban biang ka jingsynshar jong ka. La ong ba ha shuwa ka snem 1829, ym don dohlieh u ban wan kiew sha kine ki lum ba ithiang jong ngi. Ka jingsliang bad jingthrang u dohlieh ban ioh ia ka jaka ba pyngngad bad ba khiah krat ka la long kawei na ki buit treikam jong u. Ban klun ia kane ka Bri ba u tip ba ka don ia kane ka jingshisha u la thaw shibun ki buit. Nyngkong eh ula kdew iangi ba ngi dei ki “Gossiah” ka kyntien imat kaba shu khar na rithor, kaba la shu mut antad, bad ka bym ia dei dur satia bad kane ka Bri jong ngi. U Mr.Robert Lindsay, u Collector ka Sylhet, 1778, u ong ia ngi” A Tribe of Independent tartars,” ki kynhun briew ba shong sha ki thain duriaw “Casbian sea” (turk-Mongol). Baroh ar tylli ki jingring dur kim iadei dur bad ka long briew jong ngi. Ban pyniaid iew ia ka kyntien Gossiah u la pynwan dur sha “Khasi” bad kane ka kyntien la pyndonkam bad thoh, imat na ka bynta ban ai kyrteng ia ka District kaba u mut ban thaw na ka jingtohkit jong u halor kane ka kam, u la ioh lai (3) tylli ki kyntien (1) Gossiah na rithor (2) khynriam na Jaintia Hills (3) Synteng na Khasi Hills kine lai tylli ki kyntien, haduh mynta, ngim lah shem phang kumno ki la mih madan bad ki kit jingmut ia kaei?” Wat la ki long kumno kumno ruh, kine ki kyntien ki don bha ha ka shyntur u briew, ia kiba la shu khot sin khlem jingmut, bad bym iadei dur satia bad ka jaidbynriew.
