Ka kyntien kaba kit jingmut ban sngewthuh ba baroh ngi dei kawei ka Jaidbynriew, kawei ka ktien, kawei ka niam, ka riti ka dustur kam pat don, U British uba la sani bha ia ka rukom synshar (administration) u la don lypa ka jingpynkhreh ban bit ban biang ka korbar hima jong u.
Ka kyrteng tynrai jong ka ka dei Sohra, ia kaba la kynnoh "Churra" da ki phareng ha shuwa ba pynkylla ia ka sha ka kyrteng kaba mynta. Watla ka ioh u slap uba bun, hynrei ka Sohra ia ka jingeh ha kaba iadei bad ka jingduna um bad ki briew ki ju hap ban kit um na sha jngai.
Kane ka long kawei na ki jing sngewthuh bakla ba ngi don ha kaba iadei bad ka kyrteng Bhoi.
Katba ïa ka kynthei, ha ka pyrkhat khasi la niew ba ka dei ka Mei Nongpun Nongkha ban bat ia ki riti, ka niam,ka rukom, ka duh ka ïoh, ym tang kum ka khun khatduh ba la pyndonkam bakla bad batai sutra kajuk mynta ba ka dei ka nonglum bad nong pashat sbai rupa. Dei ha kaba la pynkham pynsoh ia u sai sohpet u sai longdoh jong ka longiing, long jait longkur ha ki thymmei ba jylliew bad kyntang bam jong ka jingtip ba la pasiaw ba la pyrsad da ka maia blei kumno ban pynshong ban pynneh ia ki riti ki dustur, ka niam ka rukom, ka trei ka ktah, ka lum ka lang ba kan seisoh sei syntiew ha sawdong ka lyngwiar dpei i mei, kaba ngi ong “Ka bit ka biang ka sdang na la iing.” Dei longiing ba kan neh ha ka mynnor, ka mynta bad ka lawei. Katt la pung la tang, la suit la shor ha ka long “kynthei” kaba ngi ong “I Mei”. Ka kyntien ba ia dei dor bad iajan bha bad ka jinglong Blei.
Katne ngi la leh bad trei pynban ym don jingmut ei ei, nalor kiwei kiwei ki kam bym lah niewtang. Hynrei ynda u nongwei u la wan kiew ban synshar, pynjot ia ngi la mih ban ki rukom pyniaid sianti kumno ban-sier, ban shet, ban pynpra ka Hima, ka niam bad ka longbriew manbriew jong ngi.
Ki "BHOI" ki dei ki Mikir kiba shong ba sah ha ka them Ribhoi. Bad ia ki trai shnong pat la khot ki "KAREW".
Ki Hynñiew trep
Ki nongtrei habar ka par dewiong
Kitei haneng ki dei ki kyntien shong sbai ba la ju thoh ha ki poitry bad ki jingthoh khasi ban pynpaw ia ka jinglong tylli ki paid bynriew khasi.
Kumne ngi la ïa im, ïa roi, ïapra da ki spah snem khlem kano kano ka wit ka wa ne ban ong ba kaei kaba la don bad la buh- la pynlong ki long kiba baka ka por ka la dei ban kynrong ia la ka jong, ka ud ka nam u khun bynriew ban hiar ka kyrkhu kyrdoh na jrong sha tbian lyngba ka “jingkieng ksiar” ba la buh la tang u briew u Blei naduh mynba dang kynthong ka pyrthei ki khun u Blei-u Hynniewtrep Hynniew wasa ka dei ba don bad khih ha la tyngam jong phi jong nga. Katta mynta la dawa.
Lah ban ong ruh ba ia kane ka ri them khasi la buh kyrteng Ribhoi dang myn ha u 4 tarik u June 1992.
Ngi dei ban tip bad ban kren shai da baroh ba ngi dei kawei ka jaidbynriew ba kyrpang tam ha ka pyrthei namar ia ka longiing la pynshong Blei ha pdeng “u shynrang” bad “Ka kynthei” ha kaba ka jingthew noh shiliang ka tarajur kam don, namar sha pyrthei ngi ia wan na ka Tropksiar troprupa ba la pun la sain ïa ka longbriew kat kum ka ba la buh la bynta u Nongthaw ba don sha lyndet ki Hima.
Ngi tip, ba naduh mynhyndai la don ki hima ha kane ka jaka kaba ïar naduh katei khap Kamrup shaduh shathie sha Bangladesh, bad naduh mihngi ka Mikir Hills shaduh sepngi ka Garo Hills, kine ki hima, kum ka Hima Shillong. Hima Malngiang, Hima Sutnga, Syiem Jaintiapur, Syiem Nongstoin, bad kiwei kiwei ki la iasynshar bad ia kren ia ka bit ka biang tang ha la i jong i bynta, bad kumne ki la pyniaid da ki spah snem bad la mih, la kha, bad saindur shibun ki riti ki dustur,ka ktien bad kyntien, ka riam ka beit, ka rukom nguh Blei dem Blei, bad kata ka mynsiem longdoh longsnam kaba la pynlong ia ngi ban ieit ban sngewtynnad ban shong, bad ban bei shnong-bei hima ha ki jaka ba long lum, haduh ban da tip bad khot “Riewlum” ia ngi. Ia ka kyntien “Riewlum’ hap ban ia thir iatai ban lap ia ka tyllong bashai ka nongrim longbriew jong ngi.
U Lum Sohpetbneng u dei uwei na ki lum ha ri Khasi uba don ha ki thaiñ Bhoi.
U Rangkhatar-bor, un i un da ïa la ka it ka hima, un prat ia ka lum bad ka them ban dap thiar, ban shlei u pdung, u shang u prah. Un ïeng ban bat ïa ka nia ka jutang ha ka Duwan ba la pynsakhi da u klong u skaw, u khaw-eh u khaw shan, bad ka lamet ka latang ba ïeng rangbah u briew na tbian, ap jutang u Blei na jrong. Katne la pynkup pynkham ïa ka iktir ba kyrpang u khun bynriew ha u “Khat-ar-bor” uba khih bad krih sawdong ka lyngwiar baiar u Sohpetbneng, ka pdeng pyrthei ka bri u HynñiewTrep.
Ym duna shuh ia ka 1000 snem ba ka jaidbynriew ba ngi khot mynta “Ki Khasi” ki la shong la sah ha kane ka khyndew ne jaka kaba ngi khot mynta “Ka Ri Khasi” don ruh kiba khot ia ka “Ka Bri U HynñiewTrep” bad ia ka Jaidbynriew pat ka khot “Ki Khun u HynñiewTrep.” Kine ki kyntien ba ngi ju iakren bad thoh- “Khasi” “Ri Khasi”, “Ka Bri U HynñiewTrep” bad “Ki khun U HynñiewTrep” kim ai ka jingsngewthuh kaba shai, khamtam ha ka liang ka synshar ka khaddar (politics) bad ha kaba pynïaid ïa ka Hima. (Administration).
Ynda la dep thaw ïa ka iing “Kashari” ha Shillong ha u snem 1866, la thaw (constituted) ia ka District Khasi bad Jaintia Hills. Ia kine ki kyntien “Khasi” bad “Jaintia” u la buh na ka bynta ban ithuh ia ar tylli ki khyndew bah, nangne la bud pat sa ka ban ithuh ia u ‘briew’ ktien “Ka Bri” “Ka main” bad kumta ter ter, namar ka jingsynshar (Administration) ka dei ban don bad shai bha haba ka rai bad pyndonkam ia ki ktien bad kyntien ban nym bakla ha ka jylli bishar-khadar. Ban iaid ka jingsynshar shaphrang ia ka kyntien ”Khasi” la pyndonkam bad kit sa ia ka jingmut kaba kham iar bad la pynrung ban thoh “Ka ktien Khasi” ka jaidbynriew Khasi ka “main Khasi,” kumno ngi la thoh, ïa kren bad la ïa sngewthuh ïa ki jingmut jong kine ki tien bad kyntien kiba la pyndonkam mynta la jan 170 snem kynthih.
